description: Catarina Devon known as the "Crescent Moon Hunter", was the most dangerous female pirate ever to be imprisoned in Impel Down within the entire age of pirates. She was originally imprisoned in Level 6 of Impel Down, along with other legendary criminals whose existences were erased from history. She was initially mentioned briefly by Emporio Ivankov. She has been freed by Marshall D. Teach and became the only female member of the Blackbeard Pirates.
name: Catarina Devon
